content: Dissapointed... quiz questions are multiple choice and the answer options are so unique that having a basic vocabulary allows you to answer them correctly.
It crashes every time in test mode. Great information included in learn mode.

Testing mode questions and answer selections gets stuck and pick wrong answers when tapped several times to get it unstuck. when playing audio mode the pause time is inconsistent and the 20 second intervals are inconsistent as well. Due to several abbreviations being used, it would have been better if was recorded by a human voice than a robotic voice. It will be nice, if the study could continue from where it was last left than starting all over again and if it can be installed on computer or laptops. Otherwise the content appears to align with the book and for the price, I can't complain much but if the quality is improved, it won't hurt to pay a descent price and still enjoy a good quality material.
